to run :

______
- to install rvm and ruby , curl -sSL https://get.rvm.io | bash -s stable --ruby
- to install gem , got to Gemfile directory then from command line type , bundle install
- to install chrome driver,  brew cask install chromedriver
=====
-----
DRIVER=chrome rspec -fd sample_spec/log.rb
DRIVER=firefox rspec -fd sample_spec/log.rb --format html --out report1.html

upgrade chrome driver:

brew cask upgrade chromedriver

install chrome driver: 
brew install chromedriver

install firefox driver:
brew install geckodriver
